The '''Palace''' is a building in [[ Lord of Ultima|Lord of Ultima]]. It boosts the faith for the alliance in that virtue. A Palace can only be build in a city with a [[castle]] that is enlightened by a nearby [[shrine]]. It requires a free build slot and a 3x3 area in to place it in. A palace build, once ordered, cannot be canceled or moved in the build queue. Applying shovels or keys while the palace, or any other building, is being constructed will have no affect on build speed.
